<script>
  $(function () {
    $('#buttonSend').click(function (){
      alert('빠른 시간내에 담당자가 연락 드리겠습니다.');
      location.href = '/';
    });
  });
</script>

{{> body/header-bootcamp}}
<main class="bootcamp-apply">
  <article class="head dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Bootcamp Application</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>작성된 개인 정보는 Data Science Bootcamp 진행 용도 외에는 절대로 사용되지 않습니다.</li>
        <li>Application 작성 후 선발된 인원은 개별적으로 준비 사항을 전달해드립니다.</li>
        <li>E-Mail Address 는 Gmail 사용을 권장합니다.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
  <article class="forms light">
    <div class="container">
      <section class="form">
        <h3 class="left">필수 입력 사항</h3>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="form-name">성명</span>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" aria-describedby="form-name" placeholder="성명">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="form-tel">핸드폰 번호</span>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="tel" aria-describedby="form-tel" placeholder="연락 가능한 번호">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="form-email">E-Mail</span>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="email" aria-describedby="form-email">
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="form">
        <h3 class="left">선택 입력 사항</h3>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="form-git">Git</span>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="git" aria-describedby="form-git" placeholder="url">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="form-linkedin">Linked In</span>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="linkedin" aria-describedby="form-linkedin" placeholder="url">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="form-blog">Blog</span>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="blog" aria-describedby="form-blog" placeholder="url">
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="form">
        <h3 class="left">기타 입력 사항</h3>
        <div class="input-group">
          <span class="input-group-addon" id="basic-intro">본인 소개</span>
          <textarea class="form-control" id="basic-intro" aria-describedby="basic-intro" rows="5" placeholder="Pre-Courses 수료 여부, 데이타 사이언스 경험, 프로그래밍 경험 및 직업"></textarea>
        </div>
      </section>
      <button id="buttonSend" class="btn btn-default btn-large">Send</button>
    </div>
  </article>
</main>
